{"tid":1311913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【信用系統】信用中國網站刪港澳台連結免誤會","createTime":"2019-07-13T11:28:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T15:28:26.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b528af8835da54abaa701a2300ce13e3d99cd1ba","tid":1311913,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T11:28:10.000Z","msg":"國家公共信用資訊中心設立的信用系統網站「信用中國」，在「地方信用網站」一欄，早前預留位置設港、澳、台三地的地方信用網站連結，引起外界關注，目前有關的地方網站連結現已刪除，以免出現誤會。<br />\n<br />\n政制及內地事務局長聶德權早前已澄清，有關措施與香港無關，社會信用體系絕對不會在香港實施，政府亦不會在香港施行社會信用體系。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2190917/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2190917%2F&d=ev%2BvVaAtQ3cORw7W3wlzWRZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=4a49728a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2190917/</a>"},{"pid":"be4172cb72e37cf49ba41252bcf52f61e77819d0","tid":1311913,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T11:28:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"528339b0d668de7a48a02df137fbf64a11aede72","tid":1311913,"uid":262093,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T11:29:17.000Z","msg":"又壽終正寢呀?"},{"pid":"c047fe993a1674b5b5bf027bbb3c04bc311657f8","tid":1311913,"uid":11156,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T11:30:11.000Z","msg":"信中共一成都死"},{"pid":"c96a729fe455abf827aaf48f0fde62c3c4c1e0c6","tid":1311913,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T11:30:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd7b0ecdfca4cd5852f0c93d118a616b6748a623","tid":1311913,"uid":157413,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T11:31:32.000Z","msg":"撚會信你地班狗官咩, 講一套做另一套 屌"},{"pid":"4f0886f1005e53901d79be86c122207d99532213",